curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/5124' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2084", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2084 is a CMOS, fast transient response, low  noise and high accuracy linear regulator. It is capable of  supplying 1A output current with typical dropout voltage  of only 145mV. The operating input voltage range is  from 1.5V to 5.5V. The fixed output voltage range is  from 0.55V to 4.2V and adjustable output voltage range  is from 0.55V to 5.0V.  Other features include an open-drain power-good (PG)  output, logic-controlled shutdown mode, short-circuit  current limit and thermal shutdown protection. The  SGM2084 has automatic discharge function to quickly  discharge VOUT in the disabled status.  The SGM2084 is available in a Green TDFN-2×2-6AL  package. It operates over an operating temperature  range of -40℃ to +125℃.    "}'
